# CODEOWNERS Template for Auto-Fix System
# 
# This file assigns default reviewers for auto-generated PRs.
# The PR generator agent will use this to suggest reviewers based on file paths.
#
# Format: <file-pattern> @username @team
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything (fallback)
* @maintainer-team

# Documentation changes
*.md @docs-team
docs/ @docs-team

# Configuration files
*.json @config-owners
*.yaml @config-owners
*.yml @config-owners

# Source code by area (customize for your repository)
# src/auth/ @security-team
# src/api/ @backend-team
# src/components/ @frontend-team
# src/database/ @data-team

# CI/CD and infrastructure
.github/ @devops-team
.github/workflows/ @devops-team

# Security-sensitive files (require security team review)
# .env.example @security-team
# config/secrets/ @security-team

# Package dependencies (require review)
package.json @maintainer-team
package-lock.json @maintainer-team
yarn.lock @maintainer-team
